        - fix epoch bug

0.03    Wed Feb 13 06:05:00 2013
        - override add/subtract method for providing interface like DateTime

0.02    Fri Dec 10 01:17:50 2011
        - Add today method
        - yesterday and tommorow method more faster
        - Add instance creation bug fix patch for before than Time::Piece 0.16

0.01    Sun Nov 27 01:24:38 2011
